1.00	Nika_turbina	Nika Turbina	Nika Georgievna Turbina was a Russian poet. She became famous for her profound and emotional poems which she wrote at an early age. She was writing poetry at the age of 6 and published her first book in 1984, at the age of 10. A recording of her recitations sold over 30,000 copies in the then Soviet Union.	
